  "t = 0 and t = 8 minutes": "",
  "t = 0 and t = 3 minutes": "",
  "t = 8 and t = 24 minutes": "",
  "Setting V = 0: 8t² − 24t = 0 → 8t(t − 3) = 0, so t = 0 (initially) and t = 3 minutes.": "",
  "An architect designs a room with floor area x³ + 5x² + 2x + 10 square feet. Factor this expression by grouping to find the dimensions.": "",
  "(x² + 2)(x + 5)": "",
  "(x² + 5)(x + 2)": "",
  "(x + 1)(x² + 10)": "",
  "Group as (x³ + 5x²) + (2x + 10) = x²(x + 5) + 2(x + 5) = (x² + 2)(x + 5).": ""
